commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: Everyone, that was amazing!

commands.speaker: Setsuna
commands.line: *Huff* *Puff* It felt amazing!

commands.speaker: Ai
commands.line: Yeah, It was so much fun!

commands.speaker: Karin
commands.line: It's nice going on stage with others sometimes.

commands.speaker: Kasumi
commands.line: Karin, you can just say you felt confident with me around!

commands.speaker: Shizuku
commands.line: I'm sure it was the other way around.

commands.speaker: Kasumi
commands.line: N-No it wasn't!

commands.speaker: Ayumu
commands.line: Hehe, it was a lot of fun though.

commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: I want to sing it again. Rina-chan Board says, "Harumph!"

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (It was the best performance ever. I should thank everyone who came today, but the feeling of not wanting to give up only grows stronger!)

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: Ev-ery-one!

commands.speaker: Honoka
commands.line: That was an amazing performance!

commands.speaker: Mari
commands.line: Yes! You were all so wonderful and shiny!

commands.speaker: Kotori
commands.line: I was impressed!

commands.speaker: You
commands.line: I even got goosebumps.

commands.speaker: Nozomi
commands.line: I can't just go home after seeing an awesome show like that.

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: Come on, let me and the girls do our thing, too!

commands.speaker: Kasumi
commands.line: What?!

commands.speaker: Karin
commands.line: Hehe, did we set off a competitive spark?

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: *Chuckle* Let's get everyone's eyes glued on us here in Nijigasaki, Aqours!

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: What?! We won't lose to you! Come on, let's go!

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (I can't believe a tri-show of Nijigasaki, μ's, and Aqours is happening!)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (I'm happy, but it's frustrating. I wanted to see everyone on a big stage. On the School Idol Festival stage.)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (No, it has to be at that festival. I want more and more people to see us.)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (That's why I'm not giving up.)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (Even after hearing everyone in Aqours say you have to do what you can, I was ready to just give up.)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (But now I have to make moves! I don't know what I can do, but sitting around sure won't get anything done.)

commands.speaker: [player]
commands.line: (I want to see everyone on the main stage of the School Idol Festival!)
